NAME
    Log::ger::Output::Test::Counter - Increase internal counter

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of Log::ger::Output::Test::Counter
    (from Perl distribution Log-ger-Output-Test-Counter), released on
    2020-11-17.

SYNOPSIS
     BEGIN { our $counter_get_hooks; our $counter_outputter }
     use Log::ger::Output "Test::Counter" => (
         counter_get_hooks => \$counter_get_hooks,
         counter_outputter => \$counter_outputter,
     );

DESCRIPTION
    This output is for testing only. Instead of actually outputting
    something, it increases counters.

CONFIGURATION
  counter_get_hooks
    Reference to scalar. Will be increased whenever "get_hooks" is called.

  counter_outputter
    Reference to scalar. Will be increased whenever outputter is called.

